cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use NeqSim in a publication, please cite it using these metadata."
title: "NeqSim: A library for thermodynamic and process simulation"
abstract: >
  NeqSim is an open-source Java library for thermodynamic, fluid, and process
  simulation. It supports cubic, CPA, GERG-2008, and PC-SAFT equations of
  state; full process flowsheets; PVT lab simulation; mechanical design; and
  field-development workflows.
type: software
